orderBy

void orderBy(java.lang.String name)
Add order by clause. It is possible to invoke this method several times - in this case result will be sorted by all specified fields in the correspondent order

Parameters:
name - field name by which sort should be performed

orderBy

void orderBy(java.lang.String name,
             boolean ascent)
Add order by clause. It is possible to invoke this method several times - in this case result will be sorted by all specified fields in the correspondent order

Parameters:
name - field name by which sort should be performed
ascent - true for ascent order, false for descent order
